_usage\\\": {\\n    \\\"input_tokens\\\": 257,\\n    \\\"cache_creation_tokens\\\": 287485,\\n    \\\"cache_read_tokens\\\": 23761100,\\n    \\\"output_tokens\\\": 21650,\\n    \\\"api_call_count\\\": 237\\n  },\\n  \\\"transcript_path\\\": \\\"/Users/evisdrenova/.claude/projects/..../bce82ae2-ddd8-4ee3-ae55-afeb35efbd13.jsonl\\\",\\n  \\\"first_prompt\\\": \\\"commit and push this\\\",\\n  \\\"prompt_attributions\\\": [\\n    {\\\"checkpoint_number\\\": 2, \\\"user_lines_added\\\": 0, \\\"user_lines_removed\\\": 0, \\\"agent_lines_added\\\": 0, \\\"agent_lines_removed\\\": 0},\\n    {\\\"checkpoint_number\\\": 3, \\\"user_lines_added\\\": 0, \\\"user_lines_removed\\\": 0, \\\"agent_lines_added\\\": 0, \\\"agent_lines_removed\\\": 0}\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### Complete Field Reference\\n\\nAll fields from `session.State` (lines 33-143 of `/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/session/state.go`):\\n\\n| JSON Key | Go Type | Required? | Description |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `session_id` | `string` | Yes | UUID-format session identifier |\\n| `cli_version` | `string` | No | CLI version that created session |\\n| `base_commit` | `string` | Yes | 40-char SHA of shadow branch base, updated on migration |\\n| `attribution_base_commit` | `string` | No | Original base commit for attribution, only updated after condensation |\\n| `worktree_path` | `string` | Yes | Absolute path to worktree root |\\n| `worktree_id` | `string` | No | Git worktree name (empty for main worktree) |\\n| `started_at` | `time.Time` | Yes | Session start timestamp |\\n| `ended_at` | `*time.Time` | No | When session ended (nil = still active) |\\n| `phase` | `string` | Yes | One of: `\\\"active\\\"`, `\\\"idle\\\"`, `\\\"ended\\\"` |\\n| `turn_id` | `string` | No | 12-hex-char turn identifier |\\n| `turn_checkpoint_ids` | `[]string` | No | Checkpoint IDs condensed during current turn |\\n| `last_interaction_time` | `*time.Time` | No | Updated on every hook invocation |\\n| `checkpoint_count` | `int` | Yes | Number of steps/checkpoints created |\\n| `checkpoint_transcript_start` | `int` | No | Transcript line offset for scoping |\\n| `untracked_files_at_start` | `[]string` | No | Files untracked at session start |\\n| `files_touched` | `[]string` | No | Files modified during session |\\n| `last_checkpoint_id` | `string` | No | 12-hex-char checkpoint ID from last condensation |\\n| `agent_type` | `string` | No | e.g., `\\\"Claude Code\\\"`, `\\\"Gemini CLI\\\"` |\\n| `token_usage` | `object` | No | Token usage stats |\\n| `transcript_path` | `string` | No | Path to live transcript file |\\n| `first_prompt` | `string` | No | Truncated first user prompt |\\n| `prompt_attributions` | `[]object` | No | Attribution data per checkpoint |\\n| `pending_prompt_attribution` | `object` | No | Attribution for next checkpoint |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Existing Test Helpers for Seeding Sessions\\n\\n### 1. `seedHookPerfSessions` -- The Best Reference\\n\\nFile: `/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/strategy/commit_hook_perf_test.go` (lines 253-345)\\n\\nThis is the most directly relevant helper. It seeds three categories of sessions:\\n\\n**ENDED sessions (state-file only, no shadow branch):**\\n```go\\nstate := &session.State{\\n    SessionID:           sessionID,\\n    BaseCommit:          baseCommit,\\n    WorktreePath:        dir,\\n    WorktreeID:          worktreeID,\\n    Phase:               session.PhaseEnded,\\n    StartedAt:           now.Add(-time.Duration(i+1) * time.Hour),\\n    LastCheckpointID:    cpID,          // <-- keeps them alive in listAllSessionStates\\n    StepCount:           1,\\n    FilesTouched:        modifiedFiles,\\n    LastInteractionTime: &now,\\n}\\nstore.Save(ctx, state)\\n```\\n\\n**IDLE/ACTIVE sessions (state file + shadow branch via SaveStep):**\\nUses `seedSessionWithShadowBranch()` (lines 349-401), which:\\n1. Writes modified files to disk\\n2. Creates `.entire/metadata/<sessionID>/full.jsonl` transcript\\n3.