live transcript).\\n\\n### Ref Seeding\\n\\nCreate 200 branches via go-git (`repo.Storer.SetReference`), then `git pack-refs --all`. This follows the pattern in `benchutil.SeedBranches` + `benchutil.PackRefs` (`cmd/entire/cli/benchutil/benchutil.go:555-576`).\\n\\n### Control vs Test\\n\\n**Control** (Entire disabled — no `.entire/` dir):\\n- `git add <file>` + time `git commit -m \\\"test commit\\\"` via `exec.Command`\\n\\n**Test** (Entire enabled):\\n- Set `ENTIRE_TEST_TTY=1` + create `.entire/settings.json`\\n- Write `.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG`, time `PrepareCommitMsg()` direct call\\n- Inject `Entire-Checkpoint` trailer if content-aware check skipped it\\n- `git commit -m <msg>` via CLI\\n- Time `PostCommit()` direct call\\n- Overhead = PrepareCommitMsg + PostCommit\\n\\n### Reused Code\\n\\n| Helper | File | Purpose |\\n|--------|------|---------|\\n| `session.NewStateStoreWithDir()` | `session/state.go:247` | Write state files |\\n| `id.Generate()` | `checkpoint/id/id.go:44` | Generate checkpoint IDs |\\n| `paths.ClearWorktreeRootCache()` | `paths/paths.go` | Clear cache between runs |\\n| `session.ClearGitCommonDirCache()` | `session/state.go:396` | Clear cache |\\n| `ManualCommitStrategy.SaveStep()` | `manual_commit_hooks.go` | Create shadow branches |\\n| `ManualCommitStrategy.PrepareCommitMsg()` | `manual_commit_hooks.go:295` | Timed hook |\\n| `ManualCommitStrategy.PostCommit()` | `manual_commit_hooks.go:705` | Timed hook |\\n| `trailers.CheckpointTrailerKey` | `trailers/trailers.go:41` | Trailer injection |\\n| Pattern: `repo.Storer.SetReference()` | `benchutil/benchutil.go:555` | Seed branches |\\n\\n### Expected Output\\n\\n```\\nSession templates: 10 loaded from .git/entire-sessions/\\n\\n========== COMMIT HOOK PERFORMANCE ==========\\nScenario     | Sessions | Control  | Prepare    | PostCommit | Total+Hooks  | Overhead\\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\\n100sessions  |      100 |   280ms  |     950ms  |     870ms  |      2.100s  |   1.820s\\n200sessions  |      200 |   285ms  |    1.800s  |    1.700s  |      3.785s  |   3.500s\\n500sessions  |      500 |   290ms  |    4.500s  |    4.200s  |      8.990s  |   8.700s\\n```\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n```bash\\ngo test -v -run TestCommitHookPerformance -tags hookperf -timeout 10m ./cmd/entire/cli/strategy/\\n```\\n\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1537,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":152754,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1537},\"output_tokens\":29,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYZAMUJsfxuEcGrRv9c9y\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"289a9b62-78bc-4530-b5db-1ce3afbda75d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T19:55:56.697Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"289a9b62-78bc-4530-b5db-1ce3afbda75d\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"20bfcd4a-f133-4981-8712-228da5357d19\",\"version\":\"2.1.56\",\"gitBranch\":\"sessionPruning\",\"slug\":\"clever-leaping-stream\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"The user doesn't want to proceed with this tool use. The tool use was rejected (eg. if it was a file edit, the new_string was NOT written to the file). STOP what you are doing and wait for the user to tell you how to proceed.\",\"is_error\":true,\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01NQYraomKGzRNMAhf7BStRg\"}]},\"uuid\":\"65cd7815-68d7-4875-8d18-beb55e4cfea8\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T19:58:14.190Z\",\"toolUseResult\":\"User rejected tool use\",\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"289a9b62-78bc-4530-b5db-1ce3afbda75d\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"65cd7815-68d7-4875-8d18-beb55e4cfea8\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"20bfcd4a-f133-4